These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, ebony, black, brown
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the person who likes black is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person who likes black##6
5. the person who likes black is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
6. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Color   | brown  | white | black | ebony  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, tomato, watermelon, zucchini
City: paris, colone, london, marseilles
1. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person eating zucchini##5
3. the person eating grapes is the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapes and the person eating tomato##2
5. the person eating tomato is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person traveling to paris##7
6. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person eating tomato##5
7. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person traveling to paris##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | watermelon | tomato          | zucchini | grapes     |
| City    | london      | marseilles | paris | colone |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, nurse, paramedic
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, argentine, italian, british
1. the australian is not to the left of the nurse##8
2. the argentine is on the far left##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the electrician is in an even position##4
5. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the british##5
7. the paramedic is the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | bartender | electrician | nurse     | paramedic |
| Nationality   | argentine    | british   | australian | italian    |

