.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, disco, metal, rock
House: victorian, cape-cod, modern, ranch-style
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
2. the victorian house is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
3. the modern house is on the right of the fan of disco##1
4. the fan of rock is not to the right of the modern house##8
5. the fan of blues is the victorian house##1
6. the fan of blues is on the right of the modern house##1
7. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the fan of rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | disco         | rock   | blues    |
| House         | cape-cod | ranch-style | modern | victorian |

