.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, romance, scientific
City: london, paris, prague, marseilles
1. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the person watching family movies##7
2. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching epic movies##7
4. the person watching romance movies is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
5. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person traveling to paris##7
6. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
7. the person traveling to paris is not to the left of the person watching epic movies##8
8. the person traveling to paris is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | romance | scientific | epic    |
| City         | london | marseilles   | prague   | paris |

