.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, june, may, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, rowing, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's sport is rowing##7
3. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | june      | may | august | november   |
| Sport      | badminton | rowing | volleyball  | cricket |

