.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, chess, canasta
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, rugby, tennis
1. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person playing scrabble##7
5. the person playing chess is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
6. the person playing canasta is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person playing chess##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Game     | scrabble | chess | canasta | mah-jongg     |
| Sport   | baseball   | rugby        | tennis          | ice-hockey |

