.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, librarian, manager, writer
4 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, frog, cat
1. the writer is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the frog##2
2. the owner of the snake is not the librarian##6
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the chef##1
4. the manager is not to the right of the chef##8
5. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the chef##3
6. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job         | manager | chef      | writer   | librarian  |
| Pet   | cat    | rabbit | snake | frog |

