.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, onion, pineapple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, biathlon, sailing, ice-hockey
1. the person eating onion is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
2. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is sailing##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime        | pineapple | onion      | corn    |
| Sport   | cricket | sailing   | biathlon | ice-hockey |

