.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, orange, chestnut, fuchsia
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who likes black##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
4. the person who likes black is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who likes orange##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Color   | fuchsia | orange         | chestnut    | black       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

