.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, white, ivory, turquise
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
2. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
4. the person who likes white is between the person who likes turquise and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Color   | ebony     | white | turquise        | ivory       |
| Hobby      | drawing | collecting  | card-games | magic-tricks |

