.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, scooter, van
 1. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the person driving the train##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Transport   | train | van  | scooter     | snowmobile    |

