.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, prince, dannemann
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, disco, jazz, rock
1. the fan of disco is not to the left of the game-smoker##8
2. the fan of disco is not to the left of the game-smoker##8
3. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the fan of disco##8
4. the prince-smoker is not the fan of rock##6
5. the dannemann-smoker is not to the right of the fan of rock##8
6. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
7. the prince-smoker is on the left of the fan of rock##1
8. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Cigar           | prince | dannemann | game | bluemaster   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | rock      | disco    | ambient |

