.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, orange, aquamarine, brown
1. the person who likes orange is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person who likes brown##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes mauve##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the person who likes mauve##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is between the person who likes brown and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Color   | orange | brown      | aquamarine     | mauve     |

 